#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.audiotube.appdata.xml:125
msgid ""
"AudioTube can search YouTube Music, list albums and artists, play "
"automatically generated playlists, albums and allows to put your own "
"playlist together. It is adapted to mobile phones and desktop computers."
msgstr ""
"Med AudioTube kan du søkja på YouTube Music, visa album og artistar, spela "
"automatiske genererte spelelister og album samt laga eigne spelelister. "
"Programmet er tilpassa både mobiltelefonar og datamaskiner."
